column5: Initial Design Concept design_r0 (initial design directions)

column12:
From: Michelle Marks <mmm@ideasonpurpose.com>
Subject: Re: Proxy cover/back cover design
Date: January 6, 2022 at 3:20:59 PM EST
To: Francesca De Girolami <fdegirolami@coca-cola.com>

Hi Francesca,

We’re happy to help. We’ll send a few design options for consideration, make refinements to the preferred option and then send InDesign or hi res PDF production files to TCCC or the Proxy typesetter/printer (just let us know). We’d like to get an approved ESG cover first so they can be a set, if possible. We understand this will likely need to be finalized by the first week in February.


Initial direction from client attached.
